text:
@Yuri, please use the standard summary format: category/port: <summary>, and avoid using keywords (particularly 'easy') in the summary. Each issue's 'complexity' is triaged individually.

[MAINTAINER] is also not needed. If you are maintainer, set maintainer-approval to + on the patch instead. 

You can mouse-over any flag name to see the description for that flag and what each value means/does.
